maskedData.application_description: This app will recommend solutions to improve the skin’s condition based on the results of the skin metrics report. The app will detect the skin type and provide you with recommendations on basic skin care, eye care and additional care for any particular concerns. The app will also suggest product types, such as serum, day or night cream, cleanser, etc. You can then use this information to recommend skin care cosmetics from your product line.

Use this application to analyze the skin’s overall condition.
This app will check the selfie’s image quality and assess visual skin features, such as:
  1. perceived age
  2. eye age
  3. skin tone
  4. eye bags
  5. uniformness
  6. redness
  7. wrinkles (deprecated)
  8. pores
  9. sagging (deprecated)
  10. acne
  11. pigmentation
  12. translucency
  13. hydration
  14. facial landmarks
  15. lines
For the calculated metrics, the application will produce analytics, which is available in the interface. You can use this application to compare subjects, track skin dynamics over time, and get skin metric reports.
